#Extracting and storing all filenames that end with *.csv
filenames <- list.files(path="/Users/spandana/Desktop/Datacleaning/TEDS/",pattern="*.csv")
names <- substr(filenames,1,9)

#opening the csv files and assigning them to individual dataframes 
for(i in names){
    assign(i,read.csv(paste("/Users/spandana/Desktop/Datacleaning/TEDS/",i,"_PENN.csv",sep="")))
}

#fixing the column name to YEAR in 2017 since the variable name was different in that file
names(TEDS_2017)[names(TEDS_2017)=="ADMYR"] <- "YEAR"
names(TEDS_2016)[names(TEDS_2016)=="SEX"] <- "GENDER"

#calculating the total admissions per year in PA
names_list<-as.list(strsplit(names," "))
total <- lapply(names_list,function(x){df<-get(x);df %>% filter(ROUTE1==4) %>% group_by(YEAR) %>% summarize(TOTAL_IDU=n(),TOTAL=nrow(df))})
total_df <- as.data.frame(do.call(rbind,total))

#plotting the total admissions per year in PA 
options(repr.plot.width=8, repr.plot.height=6)
total_p <- ggplot(total_df,aes(x=YEAR,y=TOTAL))+geom_line()+geom_point()+ggtitle("Total Admissions per year")+theme(plot.title=element_text(size=16,hjust=0.5))
total_p <- total_p + theme(axis.text.x=element_text(size=14),axis.text.y=element_text(size=14),axis.title.x=element_text(size=14),axis.title.y=element_text(size=14))
total_p 

#extracting information about primary route (ROUTE1) of administration
ROUTE1_year <- lapply(names_list,function(x){df <- get(x); df %>% group_by(ROUTE1,YEAR) %>% summarize(primary= n(),prop=round((n()/nrow(df))*100,digits=0))})
ROUTE1_year_df <- as.data.frame(do.call(rbind,ROUTE1_year))
ROUTE1_year_df$ROUTE1 <- recode(ROUTE1_year_df$ROUTE1,`1`="ORAL",`2`="SMOKING",`3`="INHALTN",`4`="INJECTN",`5`="OTHER",`-9`="Unknown",`20`="OTHER") 


#Plottting the primary route information
options(repr.plot.width=10, repr.plot.height=8)
R1_p <- ggplot(ROUTE1_year_df,aes(x=as.factor(YEAR),y=prop,fill=ROUTE1))+geom_bar(position="stack",stat="identity")+labs(x="ROUTE1",y="Percentage")
R1_p <- R1_p +geom_text(aes(label=paste(prop,"%")),position=position_stack(vjust=0.5), size = 4, color = "black" )
R1_p <- R1_p +theme(legend.position="right")+ theme(axis.text.x=element_text(size=14),axis.text.y=element_text(size=14))
R1_p

#Exploring relationship between substance type and IDU, frequency of use among IDU

options(scipen=999,digits=4)
ROUTE1_IDU_SUB <- lapply(names_list,function(x){df<-get(x);df%>% filter(ROUTE1==4)%>% group_by(SUB1,YEAR,FREQ1) %>% filter(n()>10) %>% summarize(TOTAL=n(),PROP=round((n()/sum(df$ROUTE1==4))*100,digits=1))})
ROUTE1_IDU_SUB_df <- as.data.frame(do.call(rbind,ROUTE1_IDU_SUB))
ROUTE1_IDU_SUB_df$SUB1 <- recode(ROUTE1_IDU_SUB_df$SUB1,`1`="NONE",`2`="ALCOHOL",`3`="COCAINE",`4`="MARIJUANA",`5`="HEROIN",`6`="NPM",`7`="OTHER OPIATES",`8`="PCP",`9`="OTHER HAL",`10`="METHAMPHETAMINE",`11`="OTHER AMP",`12`="OTHER STIM",`13`="BENZODIAZEPINES",`14`="OTHER NON-BENZODIAZEPENE TRANQS",`15`="BARBiTURATES",`16`="OTHER NON_BARB SEDATIVES",`17`="INHALANTS",`18`="OTC",`20`="OTHER",`-9`="UNKNOWN") 
ROUTE1_IDU_SUB_df$FREQ1 <- recode(ROUTE1_IDU_SUB_df$FREQ1,`1`=" NO USE IN THE PAST MONTH",`2`="1-3 TIMES IN THE PAST MONTH",`3`="1-2 TIMES IN THE PAST WEEK",`4`="3-6 TIMES IN THE PAST WEEK",`5`="DAILY",`-9`="UNKNOWN")


ggplot(ROUTE1_IDU_SUB_df,aes(x=as.factor(YEAR),y=TOTAL,fill=as.factor(SUB1)))+
        geom_bar(position="stack",stat="identity")+labs(x="YEAR")+ 
        theme(axis.text.x=element_text(size=14),axis.text.y=element_text(size=14),axis.title.x=element_text(size=14),axis.title.y=element_text(size=14))
         
        
ggplot(ROUTE1_IDU_SUB_df,aes(x=as.factor(YEAR),y=TOTAL,fill=as.factor(SUB1)))+
        geom_bar(position="stack",stat="identity")+facet_wrap(~FREQ1)+labs(x="YEAR")+
        theme(axis.text.x=element_text(size=12),axis.text.y=element_text(size=12),axis.title.x=element_text(size=14),axis.title.y=element_text(size=14))

# Exploring relationship between gender and IDU 
ROUTE1_IDU_GENDER <- lapply(names_list,function(x){df<-get(x);df%>% filter(ROUTE1==4) %>% group_by(GENDER,AGE) %>% filter(n()>10) %>% summarize(YEAR=first(YEAR),TOTAL=n())})
ROUTE1_IDU_GENDER_df <- as.data.frame(do.call(rbind,ROUTE1_IDU_GENDER))
ROUTE1_IDU_GENDER_df$GENDER <- recode(ROUTE1_IDU_GENDER_df$GENDER,`1`="MALE",`2`="FEMALE",`-9`="UNKNOWN")
ROUTE1_IDU_GENDER_df$AGE <- recode(ROUTE1_IDU_GENDER_df$AGE,`1`="12-14",`2`="15-17",`3`="18-20",`4`="21-24",`5`="25-29",`6`="30-34",`7`="35-39",`8`="40-44",`9`="45-49",`10`="50-54",`11`="55-64",`12`="65 and older")
ggplot(ROUTE1_IDU_GENDER_df,aes(x=as.factor(YEAR),y=TOTAL,fill=as.factor(GENDER)))+labs(x="YEAR")+
geom_bar(position="stack",stat="identity")+
theme(axis.text.x=element_text(size=12),axis.text.y=element_text(size=12),axis.title.x=element_text(size=14),axis.title.y=element_text(size=14))

ggplot(ROUTE1_IDU_GENDER_df,aes(x=as.factor(YEAR),y=TOTAL,fill=as.factor(GENDER)))+labs(x="YEAR")+
geom_bar(position="stack",stat="identity") +facet_wrap(~AGE)
